question.title: Error E: Package 'openjdk-11-jdk-headless' has no installation candidate when trying to install eProsima FastDDS
question.body:
I've been trying to ./install.sh eprosima fastdds 3.2.0 Linux on a Raspberry Pi but running the install always returns E: Package 'openjdk-11-jdk-headless' has no installation candidate.

I've tried apt getting the default-jre-headless, using SDKMAN! to install java 11 both with no success or change in error. I've installed eprosima fastdds on my laptop before with no issue.

I am using Debian GNU/Linux 12 (bookworm) on the Pi
